      "description": "Presenting a definitive example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, exhibiting an immaculate exterior profile and a cabin that remains in showroom state. Every mechanical component operates with absolute precision, reflecting a history of meticulous preservation. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle in truly peerless condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
